=== Access ===
* About a 30-minute walk west from {{ill|lt=Makimuku Station|Q4980794|qid=Q4980794|1=Makimuku Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Sakurai Line|Q865801|qid=Q865801|1=Sakurai Line}} of {{ill|lt=West Japan Railway Company|Q502125|qid=Q502125|lt=JR West|1=West Japan Railway Company}}
* About a 40-minute walk east from {{ill|lt=Tawaramoto Station|Q7689224|qid=Q7689224|1=Tawaramoto Station}} on the {{ill|UNKNOWN|lt=Kashihara Line|1=UNKNOWN}} of {{ill|lt=Kintetsu|Q1531085|qid=Q1531085|lt=Kintetsu Railway|1=Kintetsu Railway}}

